reviews.review:
Dr. Rabenhorst is an excellent professor.  He makes sure we all stay awake in lecture by asking a lot of questions.  He also emails us print-outs for every lecture that are basically fill-in-the-blanks with all of the stuff you need to know for quizzes and exams.
If you don't like getting dirty, don't take this class, because the lab can get pretty messy when you go out in the field.
